Package: ferobust
Title: Measurement Error Diagnostics for Fixed Effects Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Andrew", "Rosenberg", email = "andrewrosenberg@ufl.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Andrew Rosenberg
Maintainer: Andrew Rosenberg <andrewrosenberg@ufl.edu>
Description: Computes the corrected within-reliability, partial identification
    bounds, Imbens-Manski confidence intervals, the breakdown reliability, and the
    autocorrelation frontier with its certification rule for fixed-effects
    regressions with slow-moving, mismeasured regressors. Implements the reporting
    workflow from the working paper "Reliable Panel Regression: A Default Workflow
    for Slow-Moving, Mismeasured Variables."
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/asrosenberg/ferobust
BugReports: https://github.com/asrosenberg/ferobust/issues
